---
title: Carb Smart Loaded Bunless Chicken Burgers with Spinach Salad
description: Any night can be burger night, but sometimes we decide to leave the bun behind! Start with a nutritious salad base then add juicy chicken patties and pile on the pickles, crispy shallots and creamy Dijonnaise.

